{"title":"红与蓝","date":"2019-03-17T15:32:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2019年3月17日","L":"2019/03/17","MM-DD":"03-17"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/BaXoeALfGZP8q4j.jpg","link":"2019/03/17/红与蓝","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-02-10T17:04:55.669Z","content":"<blockquote><p>微风徐徐<br>田间金黄色的麦子<br>一簇簇擦着肩<br>涔涔的麦香把我留住  </p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>提着编织袋<br>沿着门前那条土路<br>悠闲地走着  </p>\n<p>袋子上印满了格子<br>蓝色的和红色的<br>沉默着像是在说话  </p>\n<p>微风徐徐<br>田间金黄色的麦子<br>一簇簇擦着肩<br>涔涔的麦香把我留住  </p>\n<p>一辆拖拉机叫嚣着过去了<br>我连忙退开<br>车上载满了一袋又一带的<br>红色和蓝色的格子  </p>\n","prev":{"title":"蜃","link":"2019/10/26/蜃"},"next":{"title":"枫","link":"2018/11/15/枫"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2019/03/17/红与蓝/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","link":"<a href=\"http://wardzhou.art/2019/03/17/红与蓝/\" title=\"红与蓝\">http://wardzhou.art/2019/03/17/红与蓝/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}